      <title>[오늘의 날씨] 2025년 12월 30일</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/29/OVZV323HVBBXZDOVUBNFQJL7GY/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/29/OVZV323HVBBXZDOVUBNFQJL7GY/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
